reviewText: Shameful.  I love Randy.  This is not a true Randy product
Bought this for a friend who loves Randy Travis.  She loved it.  Really enjoyed the songs that he sang on this DVD.
Awful quality! Randy didn't deserve that.

I'M VERY HAPPY WITH MY PURCHASE. ALWAYS ENJOY LISTENING TO RANDY'S MUSIC! HE IS THE BEST!
JANET
This dvd seems home made. I am disappointed at the quality and the length of the video. I love Randy Travis but this was a waste of money.
Do not buy this! A total rip-off! Poor quality sound and video clips. No interviews. Not as described!

The title of this dvd is really misleading.  This is not a documentary, it is just 10 concert clips of Randy's songs.  There are no "rare interviews" or "in his own words" other than Randy saying a few words before the song in Carlsbad Caverns,  Some of the video quality is really low.  Without the Tammy Wynette and George Jones songs, I would have given this dvd 1 star.
